description: BACK ON MARKET - Unit is vacant and freshly painted and move in ready! Featuring stainless steel appliances, a quartz waterfall island, and gleaming hardwood floors throughout! This unit includes an en-suite primary bedroom and a second full bath, both of which are beautifully tiled. Enjoy the convenience of in-unit laundry and central air conditioning.  Experience peaceful condo-style living with only two other units in the building and a low HOA fee due to minimal common areas to maintain! Located just minutes from the Andrew Square Red Line T station, commuting downtown or to Cambridge is effortless. Enjoy close proximity to Carson Beach, South Bay Center, and a growing lineup of local favorites like Lincoln Tavern, Fat Baby, and The Broadway. You're just a short walk to parks, bike paths, and fitness studios. Whether you're a first-time buyer, investor, or seeking a vibrant neighborhood to call home, this condo checks all the boxes
